#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.60"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.60:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.60:0.2"
msgid "6. Gotamīvagga "
msgstr "6. Gotamī "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.60:0.3"
msgid "60. Dutiyapuggalasutta "
msgstr "60. Eight People (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.293, sc1
msgctxt "an8.60:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these eight people are worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world. "

msgctxt "an8.60:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.60:1.3"
msgid "Sotāpanno, sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanno … pe … arahā, arahattāya paṭipanno. "
msgstr "The stream-enterer and the one practicing to realize the fruit of stream-entry. The once-returner and the one practicing to realize the fruit of once-return. The non-returner and the one practicing to realize the fruit of non-return. The perfected one, and the one practicing for perfection. "

msgctxt "an8.60:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassāti. "
msgstr "These are the eight people who are worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.60:2.1"
msgid "Cattāro ca paṭipannā, "
msgstr "Four practicing the path, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.2"
msgid "cattāro ca phale ṭhitā; "
msgstr "and four established in the fruit. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.3"
msgid "Esa saṅgho samukkaṭṭho, "
msgstr "This is the exalted Saṅgha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.4"
msgid "sattānaṃ aṭṭha puggalā. "
msgstr "the eight people among sentient beings. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an8.60:3.1"
msgid "Yajamānānaṃ manussānaṃ, "
msgstr "For humans, those merit-seeking creatures, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.2"
msgid "puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṃ; "
msgstr "who sponsor sacrifices, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.3"
msgid "Karotaṃ opadhikaṃ puññaṃ, "
msgstr "making merit with attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.4"
msgid "ettha dinnaṃ mahapphalan”ti. "
msgstr "what’s given here is very fruitful.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.60:3.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.60:3.6"
msgid "Gotamīvaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an8.60:4.1"
msgid "Gotamī ovādaṃ saṅkhittaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.2"
msgid "dīghajāṇu ca ujjayo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.3"
msgid "Bhayā dve āhuneyyā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.4"
msgid "dve ca aṭṭha puggalāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
